      "span_text": "Because two lineages with no genealogical, historical or surname evidence of relatedness shared the same apparent nine marker founder haplotype, we sequenced in a subset of individuals in a subset of lineages three additional single copy markers which were chosen based on high diversity statistics calculated previously [CITATION_1] : DYS449, DYS456 and DYS458."
